I’ve been on enough video calls this week to know that everyone could use a little help looking their best.
Over the past few weeks, I’ve been optimizing my own video chat setup: from knowing where to sit to get the best light, to choosing the right microphone, to just staying comfortable.
A bright screen can blow the highlights on your face out, making you look more like Casper the Ghost than a video calling champion.
If you select this option, a video preview will pop up before you enter a call to check how everything looks.
Once the call starts, I recommend hiding your video preview from yourself.